  14:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_gimbal.c ****  *   - send_write_attr_u8 (was in main.c) added here
  15:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_gimbal.c ****  *   - qx_active_gimbal set at init
  16:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_gimbal.c ****  *   - decode functions called by attr ID via hamfly_telemetry
  17:HamflyAPI/hamfly_core_gimbal.c ****  */
